1
00:00:02,249 --> 00:00:04,183
We've been waiting for you
since this morning.

2
00:00:04,384 --> 00:00:05,749
Really?

3
00:00:07,988 --> 00:00:09,979
We're waiting to welcome you
with the flowers for ages...

4
00:00:10,324 --> 00:00:12,087
Honest?
- Absolutely!

5
00:00:16,964 --> 00:00:21,731
All the way here, I had the answer
to your question memorized in my heart.

6
00:00:21,935 --> 00:00:26,065
I didn't know, I wouldn't
need to say a single word.

7
00:00:27,741 --> 00:00:31,643
Both of us have been
tied together in a bond.

8
00:00:32,146 --> 00:00:35,081
Where can you go?

9
00:00:44,458 --> 00:00:47,757
Come on, kids.
Have some fresh guavas!

10
00:00:52,466 --> 00:00:58,098
You'll find a lot of Rajasthani
color in our attire and speech.

11
00:00:58,906 --> 00:01:03,502
My heart is overjoyed to see you.

12
00:01:04,545 --> 00:01:07,446
What are you explaining to her?

13
00:01:07,714 --> 00:01:10,410
She has lived abroad.

14
00:01:10,751 --> 00:01:13,242
I'm introducing her to the village.

15
00:01:14,621 --> 00:01:19,081
I've heard that people in
the cities are so busy...

16
00:01:19,326 --> 00:01:23,285
