here nor mobile phones.

22
00:01:45,419 --> 00:01:47,011
There's a shortage of electricity!

23
00:01:47,321 --> 00:01:50,722
We've left the electricity way behind.

24
00:01:52,292 --> 00:01:54,726
We're going for a walk.

25
00:01:56,330 --> 00:01:57,957
Coming.

26
00:01:58,899 --> 00:02:01,163
Come on.
- You go ahead.

27
00:02:01,401 --> 00:02:03,961
I'll help the ladies in the kitchen.

28
00:02:07,007 --> 00:02:09,134
