but here we're running!

35
00:02:29,329 --> 00:02:31,160
Shall we return?
- Just a little further.

36
00:02:31,431 --> 00:02:33,524
I want to show Prem how far
the factory has progressed.

37
00:02:34,534 --> 00:02:36,434
Prem, come on.

38
00:02:36,670 --> 00:02:38,331
Come on.

39
00:03:06,366 --> 00:03:07,958
This is the site.

40
00:03:08,135 --> 00:03:10,831
Production will begin in a few months.

41
00:03:12,839 --> 00:03:16,741
Can we check the progress of the
factory from close quarters later?

42
00:03:17,010 --> 00:03:19,535
I'm feeling terribly cold!

43
