Okay, we'll sit here for sometime.

44
00:03:24,551 --> 00:03:29,113
Won't Papa be terribly happy
when the factory is operational.

45
00:03:30,924 --> 00:03:32,687
What are you thinking of?

46
00:03:32,893 --> 00:03:36,761
Nothing.
- I think he's starving.

47
00:03:37,931 --> 00:03:40,866
Go for a run. I have to
talk to Prem about something.

48
00:03:41,168 --> 00:03:43,796
