on the faces of people.

54
00:04:06,193 --> 00:04:09,219
Don't you then feel...

55
00:04:09,663 --> 00:04:13,622
What is all this for?

56
00:04:14,501 --> 00:04:17,868
Sometimes I feel my education,
my Masters Degree...

57
00:04:21,007 --> 00:04:22,804
Everything seems futile.

58
00:04:22,976 --> 00:04:25,968
We can't run away from the truth.

59
00:04:26,246 --> 00:04:29,841
Will your thinking
diminish somebody's sorrow?

60
00:04:30,450 --> 00:04:32,941
If you want to share their sorrow...

61
00:04:33,387 --> 00:04:37,289
Do something that will
bring joy to their lives.

62
00:04:38,492 --> 00:04:41,893
Look at this plant.
When it is operational...

63
00:04:42,362 --> 00:04:44,887
This place will always have power.

64
00:04:45,599 --> 00:04:48,568
This is Papa's dream.
For the progress of this village.

65
00:04:49,803 --> 00:04:54,206
